---
title: Caramelized Veggie Kebabs with Summer Corn Relish and Couscous
description: Kebabs are made for summer—they’re easy, transportable, and perfect for the grill! These veggie skewers are loaded up with mushrooms, zucchini, and bell peppers, then popped under the broiler for major caramelization. A side of tangy corn relish is the perfect accompaniment!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/caramelized-veggie-kebabs-b7376bd0.jpg
